para_trans: Government Decision Number: Narrow-2025 / E-1297119 / VISHI-3
The scope of this task force group will be as follows.
I. Long-term goals - Maharashtra @ 2047 (d. August 15, 2047): India's Centenary Celebrations
Objectives to be achieved.
Medium-term goals - Maharashtra @ 75 (Dt. May 1, 2035): - The Amrit Mahotsav of Maharashtra
Objectives to be achieved.
Short-term goals - Five-year / year-wise goals: - D. October 02, 2029 in the next five years
Goals to be achieved year-wise.
IV. Progressive, sustainable, inclusive and good governance to promote regional development of the state.
The task force group should create a vision document with four such key pillars at the centre.
V. Challenges, Opportunities, and Changing Technologies in 2029, 2025, and 2047
The workforce group should consider.
The Government Order is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
